$OpenBSD: patch-Makefile,v 1.2 2021/11/10 13:31:46 jca Exp $

don't link libdl
look in LOCALBASE for libs and headers
remove -Ofast
honor CXXFLAGS
don't hardcode clang++

Index: Makefile
--- Makefile.orig
+++ Makefile
